  "slug": "husks-drop-sand",
  "title": "Husks Drop Sand",
  "description": "Husks drop sand upon death",
  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yMkEnaL.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/mars_\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/ko--fi-donate-FF5E5B?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=ko-fi&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on ko-fi\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/husks-drop-sand\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/476656?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/husks-drop-sand\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/husks-drop-sand?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This fully configurable mod adds a chance for husks to drop sand when they die. Since husks spawn in deserts, it only makes sense that they would have some sand stuck in them. It's a simple tweak that enables balanced overworld sand farms—no need to tear up entire deserts. &nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ESe7V8v.gif\" /></p></center>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Configuration</strong></summary>\n<p>You can configure this mod directly in-game or edit the JSON file <code>config/huskssand.json</code> in your profile folder. If you're using Fabric and want to adjust the config values in-game, you'll need to install <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu\">Mod Menu</a>. Please note that any changes will require restarting Minecraft to take effect.</p>\n<center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>min_rolls</b> - Sets the minimum number of sand blocks that can be dropped</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>max_rolls</b> - Sets the maximum number of sand blocks that can be dropped</p>\n</center>\n</details>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://url-shortener.curseforge.com/hGkcB\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/y3LiTfU.png\"/></a></p>\n",
